<br>
Camping does not require skill at all.  Taking out fire giants doesn't.  Camping grimblox or bergurgle doesn't.  It requires  peeps to help with ports, or with buffs such as eb or having special equipment to do the quest a little easier.  It requires mobilizing forces to take the Zordak at whatever time he spawns. It takes being awarded the overking note in chardok when on an chardok royal raid.  <br>
<br>
With this new spawn of Zordak and the promises of FCFS from other guilds and people, it is sad that only clerics from guilds with a great deal of support will be eligible.  Zordak is a harder mob now, does AOE fire of 600 and hits for 650...larger and higher level forces required.<br>
<br>
Hence rez sticks will be fewer and when someone needs an extra cleric froma smaller guild to support a uber mob encounter chances are they will not have rez sticks.  Is actually a loss for all of prexus.  Added rez sticks in game helps everyone. <p><center>
